local variable are define inside the method,memory gets allocated when method starts execution and memory gets deallocated when method stops execution.

global variable are decalred with the "global" keyword.


Example:-
	variable1 = 'indra'
	def sample():
		print variable1		// o/p:-'indra'
	print variable1			// o/p:-'indra'
	sample()	
	print variable1			// o/p:-'indra'
